Client: Luxury Serviced Apartment Brand (Feb 2026)
Built 7 automated communication workflows for a luxury serviced apartment operator targeting corporate clients, embassies, and
VIPs.

The 7 workflows:
1. Booking Confirmation (Email + WhatsApp)
2. Pre-Arrival Welcome — 48hrs before check-in (Email + WhatsApp)
3. Check-In Day Message (WhatsApp)
4. Mid-Stay Check-In — 48hrs after check-in (WhatsApp)
5. Post-Stay Review Request — 24hrs after check-out (Email + WhatsApp)
6. Re-Booking Offer — 14 days post check-out (Email)
7. Corporate Follow-Up — new corporate contact (Email)

CRM integration | WhatsApp Business API | Email automation | Delivered as ready-to-import workflow files

